Class OrbPartitionManager<M extends PartitionProcess>

java.lang.Object
  org.goldenorb.OrbPartitionManager<M>
Type Parameters:
M - The class of PartitionProcess that will be launched by OrbPartitionManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
OrbConfigurable
public class OrbPartitionManager<M extends PartitionProcess>
extends Object
implements OrbConfigurable

OrbPartitionManager launches partitions via the proxy object PartitionProcess. It communicates with OrbPartitionMember processes via Hadoop RPC.
